data.name: Urborg, Tomb of Yawgmoth
data.oracle_text: Each land is a Swamp in addition to its other land types.
data.flavor_text:
"Yawgmoth's corpse is a wound in the universe. His foul blood seeps out, infecting the land with his final curse."
—Lord Windgrace
